  <p>Hi, I&rsquo;m Brendan, a freelance web designer and developer based in Lincolnshire. I deliver across a broad range of disciplines including branding, illustration, layout design, art direction, interaction design and front-end development. This makes me something of a creative generalist, and I&rsquo;m at my best when given freedom to roam.</p>
  <p>At the heart of <a href="/services">my craft</a> is a keen focus on building technology that can make people’s lives better in a big way every day. I enjoy working with teams that foster creativity and put their customers first. It doesn’t matter how big or small your company is, if you’re passionate about your business and want to get the most from your website, you’re already a dream client and I’d love to hear from you.</p>
</div>
